===Adjective===
'''apocryphal'''

# of dubious veracity
# of doubtful authenticity
# like the nature of an urban legend/myth (i.e. there is nothing fantasy-like or unreal about it so it could be true, but based on factors like its incredulous nature it probably is false.)
# non-canonical
